The paper focuses on the application of integer programming to path-based optimization problems in robotics, which falls under the scope of robotics (cs.RO). The paper also discusses the use of optimization techniques and algorithms, which are commonly associated with artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG).
